# 2. NAKED DOMAIN REDIRECT (Forces WWW and HTTPS)
# Redirects the naked domain to the secure, primary domain.
http://ryzethakidd.com/* https://www.ryzethakidd.com/:splat 301!

# 3. HTTP TO HTTPS (Forces SSL/Security on the primary domain)
# Forces HTTPS on the primary domain.
http://www.ryzethakidd.com/* https://www.ryzethakidd.com/:splat 301!

